{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":269,"text":"So recently,"},{"time":2374,"text":"some white guys and some black women"},{"time":5176,"text":"swapped Twitter avatars, or pictures online."},{"time":7808,"text":"They didn't change their content,"},{"time":9093,"text":"they kept tweeting the same as usual,"},{"time":10904,"text":"but suddenly, the white guys noticed"},{"time":13702,"text":"they were getting called the n-word all the time"},{"time":15603,"text":"and they were getting the worst kind of online abuse,"},{"time":18331,"text":"whereas the black women all of a sudden"},{"time":20891,"text":"noticed things got a lot more pleasant for them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23962,"text":"Now, if you're my five-year-old,"},{"time":25897,"text":"your Internet consists mostly of puppies and fairies"},{"time":29130,"text":"and occasionally fairies riding puppies."},{"time":31285,"text":"That's a thing. Google it."},{"time":34030,"text":"But the rest of us know that the Internet"},{"time":36324,"text":"can be a really ugly place."},{"time":39182,"text":"I'm not talking about the kind of colorful debates"},{"time":42157,"text":"that I think are healthy for our democracy."},{"time":44445,"text":"I'm talking about nasty personal attacks."},{"time":47823,"text":"Maybe it's happened to you, but it's at least"},{"time":49947,"text":"twice as likely to happen, and be worse,"},{"time":52738,"text":"if you're a woman, a person of color, or gay,"},{"time":54741,"text":"or more than one at the same time."},{"time":56675,"text":"In fact, just as I was writing this talk,"},{"time":59364,"text":"I found a Twitter account called @SallyKohnSucks."},{"time":64343,"text":"The bio says that I'm a"},{"time":67215,"text":"\"man-hater and a bull dyke and the only\nthing I've ever accomplished with my career"},{"time":70724,"text":"is spreading my perverse sexuality.\""},{"time":73289,"text":"Which, incidentally, is only a third correct."},{"time":75466,"text":"I mean, lies! (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"But seriously, we all say we hate this crap."},{"time":83113,"text":"The question is whether you're willing to make"},{"time":84930,"text":"a personal sacrifice to change it."},{"time":88118,"text":"I don't mean giving up the Internet."},{"time":89980,"text":"I mean changing the way you click,"},{"time":92182,"text":"because clicking is a public act."},{"time":95037,"text":"It's no longer the case"},{"time":96710,"text":"that a few powerful elites control all the media"},{"time":99121,"text":"and the rest of us are just passive receivers."},{"time":101360,"text":"Increasingly, we're all the media."},{"time":104172,"text":"I used to think, oh, okay, I get dressed up,"},{"time":107332,"text":"I put on a lot of makeup,"},{"time":109238,"text":"I go on television, I talk about the news."},{"time":111116,"text":"That is a public act of making media."},{"time":114457,"text":"And then I go home and I browse the web"},{"time":116516,"text":"and I'm reading Twitter,"},{"time":117652,"text":"and that's a private act of consuming media."},{"time":119769,"text":"I mean, of course it is. I'm in my pajamas."},{"time":122326,"text":"Wrong."},{"time":124152,"text":"Everything we blog, everything we Tweet,"},{"time":126266,"text":"and everything we click"},{"time":129621,"text":"is a public act of making media."},{"time":132937,"text":"We are the new editors."},{"time":134481,"text":"We decide what gets attention"},{"time":136313,"text":"based on what we give our attention to."},{"time":139110,"text":"That's how the media works now."},{"time":140457,"text":"There's all these hidden algorithms that decide"},{"time":142870,"text":"what you see more of and what we all see more of"},{"time":145133,"text":"based on what you click on,"},{"time":146890,"text":"and that in turn shapes our whole culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150956,"text":"Over three out of five Americans think we have"},{"time":152911,"text":"a major incivility problem in our country right now,"},{"time":156901,"text":"but I'm going to guess that at least three out of five"},{"time":158635,"text":"Americans are clicking on the same insult-oriented,"},{"time":162655,"text":"rumor-mongering trash that feeds"},{"time":164803,"text":"the nastiest impulses in our society."},{"time":167860,"text":"In an increasingly noisy media landscape,"},{"time":171833,"text":"the incentive is to make more noise to be heard,"},{"time":175213,"text":"and that tyranny of the loud"},{"time":178140,"text":"encourages the tyranny of the nasty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181477,"text":"It does not have to be that way."},{"time":184395,"text":"It does not."},{"time":185957,"text":"We can change the incentive."},{"time":188832,"text":"For starters, there are two things we can all do."},{"time":190452,"text":"First, don't just stand by the sidelines\nwhen you see someone getting hurt."},{"time":194385,"text":"If someone is being abused online, do something."},{"time":198065,"text":"Be a hero. This is your chance."},{"time":200194,"text":"Speak up. Speak out. Be a good person."},{"time":202545,"text":"Drown out the negative with the positive."},{"time":204841,"text":"And second, we've got to stop clicking"},{"time":208230,"text":"on the lowest-common-denominator, bottom-feeding"},{"time":210633,"text":"linkbait."},{"time":211999,"text":"If you don't like the 24/7 all Kardashian"},{"time":215571,"text":"all the time programming,"},{"time":217253,"text":"you've got to stop clicking on the stories"},{"time":219127,"text":"about Kim Kardashian's sideboob."},{"time":223070,"text":"I know you do it. (Applause)"},{"time":225874,"text":"You too, apparently."},{"time":227814,"text":"I mean, really, same example:"},{"time":228939,"text":"if you don't like politicians calling each other names,"},{"time":231436,"text":"stop clicking on the stories"},{"time":233147,"text":"about what one guy in one party called\nthe other guy in the other party."},{"time":236207,"text":"Clicking on a train wreck just pours gasoline on it."},{"time":238998,"text":"It makes it worse, the fire spreads."},{"time":240920,"text":"Our whole culture gets burned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244917,"text":"If what gets the most clicks wins,"},{"time":248050,"text":"then we have to start shaping the world we want"},{"time":250921,"text":"with our clicks,"},{"time":252890,"text":"because clicking is a public act."},{"time":256776,"text":"So click responsibly. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259256,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}